# Boot counter rollback: reset to 0 if exceeds limit.
*tick(c as i64, lim as i64) returns i64
    if c + 1 >= lim
        return 0
    c + 1

*after(n as i64, lim as i64) returns i64
    c is 0
    i is 0
    while i < n
        c is tick(c, lim)
        i is i + 1
    c

*main
    log after(7, 5)
    log after(11, 5)
